[+] Usage 

C:\Documents\python Creep.py -h
usage: Creep.py [-h] [-all] number

Scan a Phone-Number and retrieve its information

positional arguments:
  number               The Phone-Number to scan

options:
  -h, --help           show this help message and exit
  -all, --all-results  Print all Geo-Location results

example : python Creep.py +<countryNumber><number> or add the -all flag to get more geolocation results

